{"tid":687064,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤哥真係好吸引？🙄","createTime":"2018-06-02T01:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T14:55:07.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ace0e88a9d7617aa95b6623d2d02e6189d829b93","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:54:44.000Z","msg":"陳慧琳都要主動打招呼，水著女優又扮親熱 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66f44e132217c1939e7585aa7f36457481137d23","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"陳慧琳主動打招呼　坤哥尷尬面紅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P4jM_BbehSo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP4jM_BbehSo&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=fa17a157\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P4jM_BbehSo</a>"},{"pid":"8b6487698e231b85bc38efd912b90c480c8261a7","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T01:57:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">坤哥同水 女優合作搏到盡</span><br />\n<br />\n坤哥昨日到電台為新歌《精裝追女仔》宣傳，剛巧遇上同是到電台宣傳新歌的前輩陳慧琳（Kelly），Kelly更主動跟坤哥打招呼，即時令坤哥尷尬得面紅耳赤，之後二人更來個握手合照。<br />\n<br />\n早前坤哥與10位日本女模合作拍攝MV，還跟其中一位水 女優扮親熱，坤哥解釋只是做幻想出來的畫面，所以會有一些餵食及挑逗他的動作出現。問到可有取得女模電話？他則稱沒有，但遲些會有網上選舉，網民投選出最愛那一位女模，之後女模會來港出席坤哥的活動。"},{"pid":"7c529a47e6aef186f1679e1f997400a9b0084c4b","tid":687064,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fb1f7fd6a54c6abbbace77cdfd22983e82b2369","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"追問他拍攝時有否抑壓自己或把持不住？坤哥笑言：「保持自我，]要表現紳士。哈哈！」他更笑指在片內硬 頭皮，因為要跳舞，所以拼盡畢生精力去跳。"},{"pid":"59dc23fa3ef7c2c75035cf7c152c2daabab211ec","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"「赴日做硬漢子　吳業坤咀女優：拼盡精力」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fJkQ6WtmNts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfJkQ6WtmNts&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b32be03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fJkQ6WtmNts</a>"},{"pid":"9f57eb638a5ea03cdfa17fff5245ae83c4e4bfc1","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個</blockquote><br />\n牙坤<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ff3c9d48fa993d64a7fc94dbb4349e4bdbd92a","tid":687064,"uid":81698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:18:51.000Z","msg":"廣告post please report and block"},{"pid":"fe271182d02cd32aee13f2adf2022d1ed4cda9f0","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣告post please report and block</blockquote><br />\n是愚樂新聞<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03822162555470d2a40b9d136ff3fd2aa0a4947b","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"他說︰「我的童年心願就是認識日本女生。這10位女模各有姿色，拍攝時一個餵我吃東西，<span style=\"color: red;\">一個挑逗我小弟弟</span>，我意思是我是小弟弟﹗其中一場，我更與比堅尼女優借位親吻（把持得住？）當然，很緊張，而且我要保護香港男生的形象，硬住頭皮去跳舞。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F065158_924e0e8e0725bc0876d3b3627943a4ca.png&h=11bd3f15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72ffeadbc5df8a0f621b9a250a3fc3a0d9bcfc26","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"「坤哥向緋聞說「不不不不不」！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UY0WBsXgql0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUY0WBsXgql0&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e8b45415\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UY0WBsXgql0</a>"},{"pid":"5dab2272c167dae9a75fd30d655ff9fc8c152122","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「坤哥向緋聞說「不不不不不」！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UY0WBsXgql0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUY0WBsXgql0&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e8b45415\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UY0WBsXgql0</a></blockquote><br />\n精於追女仔 定 精裝追女仔 喎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2833c1285930db32b230ef5162073117bf27672","tid":687064,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"毒絲表示覺得佢幾可愛"},{"pid":"a7bdb1c90ed02a827eb4f4569212f593018511ec","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒絲表示覺得佢幾可愛</blockquote><br />\n叫佢坤坤好嗎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5534014abf79b107e93b249a02c321573c762aaa","tid":687064,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53256b7ba3ed7a754030ac6658889c0248e570ea","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"轉灣定轉彎？牙坤字都未寫好教做人道理<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4KUR-0191a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4KUR-0191a8&d=RNTYwoD92dtDUkm2%2B7mGEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=108a57ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4KUR-0191a8</a><br />\n<br />\n坤哥去咗日本渡假，除咗食同買之外，佢仲去埋滑雪添，佢放咗段片上社交網站，睇落都有姿勢有實際嘅，不話佢個標題就成為熱話，皆因佢話：「做人同滑雪一樣要學識轉灣。」，無錯，就係個「灣」字出問題喇，網民留言話佢「轉灣」定「轉彎」都唔識，應該要學寫字先，再加上條片只係影佢直衝，網民就回應：「幾好喎！後生仔係要衝下」。"},{"pid":"a610b73d7809f398fded4106019bb18f70df1865","tid":687064,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"佢食屎啦 唔想見呢條撚樣 好撚假"},{"pid":"5c449e3b6d22446baaa2bc3ffa535e55ca2404f0","tid":687064,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"個個都要痴坤哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c2a3696306e159e22c61baa2aaea3181a8d4f6","tid":687064,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"牙坤!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/072338_8552a494fb26c671de7a260ecdc13af3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2